meaning_str.bing:
v. 保护；防护；（制定法律）保护；（通过征关税）保护（国内企业）
网络. 保卫；警戒；护盾

保护；防护；（制定法律）保护；（通过征关税）保护（国内企业）

保护；防护；投保；为…买保险；对…实行贸易保护；（计算机）保护（数据或储存库）

1.en: this moment I declare the vendetta against you, so protect yourself as well as you can, for the next time we meet your last hour has come.
1.cn: 从我向你宣布为亲人复仇的这个时候起，你就赶紧想法保护你自己吧，因为下一次我再碰见你的时候，你死期就到了。

2.en: Ship is the place for him to protect himself and imprison himself, also isolated him with the rest of the world.
2.cn: 船就是他保护自己，囚禁自己的地方，同时也是他与红尘隔离的地方。

3.en: She had fought for years trying to pass a bill to protect women against domestic violence.
3.cn: 她曾试图争取年内通过一项法案，以保护妇女免受家庭暴力。

0.cn: 你要保护我不受她的影响吗？

1.en: I guess they thought I could protect them.
1.cn: 我想他们是觉得我能保护他们。

2.en: And Hammond won't be there to protect you this time.
2.cn: 哈蒙德这次可保护不了你。

3.en: We'll protect the kingdom, my lord. You and I.
3.cn: 我们会保护王国的，陛下，你和我。

4.en: I want to protect people like you. Like us.
4.cn: 我想保护像你这样的人，像我们这样的人。

5.en: To protect your pet dragon? Are you serious?
5.cn: 就为了保护你的宠物龙? 你是认真的吗?

6.en: You're saying they'll come for me. We would protect you.
6.cn: 你是说他们会来抓我？我们会保护你的。

7.en: Where were you, Charles? We were supposed to protect them!
7.cn: 你当时又在哪？查尔斯，我们应该保护他们。

8.en: You wanna live here? You need a people to protect you. Only I can protect you, and I will, for a price.
8.cn: 要想呆在这儿，你得有个能保护你的族群，只有我行，开个好价我就答应保护你。

9.en: So, you want to protect your power at the expense of the patients. I want to protect the patients at the expense of my power.
9.cn: 那么，你想保护你的权力不惜牺牲你的病患，而我想牺牲我的权力去保护病患。

10.en: I was not able to protect my father from you, but I will protect the prince and the kingdom no matter what becomes of me.
10.cn: 我未能保护我的父亲免于你的伤害，但不管我会遭遇什么，我都要保护王子和这国家。

11.en: He attacked our friend, and her husband protected her, and now we are gonna protect them.
11.cn: 袭击了咱的朋友，而她老公出手保护了她，轮到咱们保护他们了。

12.en: If he's trying to protect her in any way, it exposes him.
12.cn: 如果他想保护玛格丝，就有可能暴露弱点。

13.en: It's Farkle who's always loved us and tried to protect us.
13.cn: 法尔科才是一直关爱我们想要保护我们的人。

14.en: Bound for greatness, destined to protect the people of New York.
14.cn: 因伟大而生，为保护纽约的人民而生 。

15.en: Why would I do that? I'm trying to protect both you and I.
15.cn: 我为什么要那样? 我这是在保护我们两个人。

16.en: How can I protect the king when I can hardly wipe my own ass?
16.cn: 我连自己的屁股都擦不干净，还怎么保护国王？

17.en: And a lot of powerful men with a desire to preserve peace and protect life.
17.cn: 许多掌权者都想要保卫和平，保护生命。

18.en: I'm trying to protect us both. These are questions anyone could ask.
18.cn: 我想保护我们两个人，这些问题是人都会问的。

19.en: Her name is yours. Kokachin. I will protect that name. And you.
19.cn: 她的名字就是你的，阔阔真，我会保护那个名字，还有你。
